there is a drain on the bottom of the top bucket. Just to keep big chunks from going thru :

![image|690x920](upload://aHROOz8ncc8RiP9FG7AigPZPqYA.jpeg) 

![image|690x920](upload://gydaOrgqtnrA8f51lAz6QxqgwTF.jpeg) 

